lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Svetlana Kuznetsova advanced to the quarterfinals of the Prague Open by beating unseeded Madison Brengle 5-7, 6-4, 6-3 on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Kuznetsova, Safarova Reach Quarterfinals at Prague Open
